Package: TopTreeSegR
Type: Package
Title: Topological Tree Segmentation using Discrete Morse Theory
Version: 1.0.0
Author: Gergo Dioszegi
Maintainer: Gergo Dioszegi <dijogergo@gmail.com>
Description: Ultra-fast topology-based tree segmentation from LiDAR point clouds 
    using Discrete Morse Theory and RcppArmadillo. Provides blazing-fast gradient 
    flow analysis for efficient individual tree segmentation.
